description: Get details for a Bring Your Own License (BYOL) subscription that's registered to your account.

parameters.name: SubscriptionProviderArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the BYOL registration resource to get details for.

nested_items.name: LastSuccessfulDataRetrievalTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp from the last time License Manager retrieved subscription details from your registered third-party Linux subscription provider.

nested_items.name: SecretArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the third-party access secret stored in Secrets Manager for the BYOL registration resource specified in the request.

nested_items.name: SubscriptionProviderArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the BYOL registration resource specified in the request.

nested_items.name: SubscriptionProviderSource
nested_items.description: The subscription provider for the BYOL registration resource specified in the request.

nested_items.name: SubscriptionProviderStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the Linux subscription provider access token from the last successful subscription data request.

nested_items.name: SubscriptionProviderStatusMessage
nested_items.description: The detailed message from your subscription provider token status.
